common_filenames.description: [YYYY.MM.DD_HH-MM-SS-TZA].wdmon - A WDMON file is named according to the time in which it is created. For example, a WDMON file saved at 1:13:43pm on July 10, 2020 in the Central Daylight Time (CDT) zone will be named 2020.07.10_13-13-43-CDT.wdmon .
